{"tid":844852,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"錯既時間遇上啱既人","createTime":"2018-10-02T07:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T08:33:23.000Z","uid":213708,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4770b4f8c19e3e60c59b8d2d09a31411d13705","tid":844852,"uid":213708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"中學因為小小好感一齊左 <br />\n但之後因為對其他人既新鮮感而忽略左佢<br />\n佢都不離不棄<br />\n直到grad之後佢捱唔住要分手<br />\n本來以為自己睇得開可以搵過個所以分左冇挽留<br />\n但過左一年經歷過新戀情之後先發現好愛佢想追番<br />\n但我冇方法搵到佢<br />\n究竟我應該向前望放低佢<br />\n定係繼續乜都唔理咁等佢追番佢<br />\n冇左佢日日都好頹 <br />\n學又唔番運動都冇心機做<br />\n<br />\n時間一走左就番唔到轉頭<br />\n係一個唔成熟既時候遇上真既愛情<br />\n結果走左先黎後悔莫及<br />\n希望各位巴絲好好珍惜身邊佢<br />\n等啱既人可以一直陪伴你到啱既時間<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"b08221302d83279ae59b6c5d7e2394a088afe54b","tid":844852,"uid":118052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:42:12.000Z","msg":"gay"},{"pid":"b68ebae70fdd7d8d73db1773a5f2d30c35943a71","tid":844852,"uid":82398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"借口 花心就花心啦"},{"pid":"7afaca50649522145b91d89bf3713b116cd701d2","tid":844852,"uid":19062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"放過人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ffb3f8d90dc19f1e65fdebc4c4f691a53dfbdf","tid":844852,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"72ddd06916df8b9cff9f1a22efc0b2f9d9a12929","tid":844852,"uid":28737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:47:23.000Z","msg":"講真 唔好再害人 你咎由自取的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ca125c4f457ff6bcafa15ca6a328332b033948","tid":844852,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:48:17.000Z","msg":"我屌緊你條女 好撚爽"},{"pid":"926b065e1c3bef1e7b7e9c63960f83043d1369d9","tid":844852,"uid":214008,"like":0,"dislike":0,